    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BRAnIFF InTERnATIOnAL\nU.S. MAINLAND HAWAII MEHICO SOUTH AMERICA\nYou'll like flying\n.............. O-\nBraniff Style.\nBRANIFF InTERNATIONAL\nB/\nSummer/ Fall 1971",
      "Braniff flies the good times\nbetween Dallas/Fort Worth\nand LaGuardia\nDallas/Fort Worth to LaGuardia, 8:45 A.M., 12:15 Noon, 5:30 P.M\nLaGuardia to Dallas/Fort Worth,\n9:00 A.M.,\n2:15 P.M., 5:30 P.M.\nThe good times start with Braniff's 8:45 a.m. non-stop. It's the most convenient early morning flight\nfrom Dallas/Fort Worth to LaGuardia, Manhattan's close-in airport. And\nat 5:30 p.m., you can\ntake advantage of our late-afternoon non-stop to LaGuardia after a full day's business. We give you good\ntimes back to Dallas/Fort Worth, too.\nPhone Braniff. We'l put you up in style to Kennedy or Newark airport if you preter. We'll get you a con-\ntirmed reservation in tive seconds. And arrange a room or rental car, too. It's all part of flying Braniff Style.",
      "Scheduled Services\nRoute Map\nPortland.\nI Buffalo\n| Cleveland\n| Boston\nNew York/Newark\nOmaha\n• San Francisco/Oakland\nColorado Sonahoma\n• Los Angeles\n• Atlanta\nCorpus Christi\na/ St. Petersburg/Clearwate\nMiami/For Lauderdal\nMexico City\nAcapulco\nTo Honolulu • To Hilo\nCaracas\n• Brasilia\n• Cochabamba\nBRANIFF INTERNATIONAL\nU.S. MAINLAND\nHAWAII\nSOUTH AMERICA\n• Belo Horizonte\n• Rio de Janeiro\nSao Paulo\n• Porto Alegre\nI Valparaiso\nSantiago\n• Concepcion\n• Montevideo"
